A developer can integrate Notifuse by updating transactional email templates via its UI and sending emails with a simple API call. For example, using the Notifuse Golang or React SDK, you can send an email like this:

go
import "github.com/notifuse/notifuse/client"

// Initialize the client
client := client.New("YOUR_API_KEY")

// Send a transactional email
response, err := client.SendTransactionalEmail({
    To: "user@example.com",
    Subject: "Welcome to Notifuse",
    TemplateID: "welcome_template",
})
